# Workspace Guidelines

## General
- IMPORTANT: Please do not run the code reformat command yourself. I will do it later.
- ALWAYS respond in Vietnamese.

## Coding style
- Follow PSR-12 standard for PHP.
- Avoid using `var_dump`, use `pr($a)` instead.

## Framework
- Prefer official NukeViet libraries.
- Avoid importing unverified third-party libraries.

## Best practices
- Add comments for all public functions.
- All code must pass `phpcs` before commit.
